                     <interp inst="t18200412-35-person368" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's shopman. Dunbar came into the shop when the prisoner ran out. I took the sheeting from him; it cost 3 l. 12 s.</p>
               <p>GEORGE SHIPLING. I am a watchman. I heard the cry of Watch! and assisted in securing the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
